From the hospital.

289
00:14:41,740 --> 00:14:42,980
They give flowers at discharge.

290
00:14:45,900 --> 00:14:47,180
Alright.

291
00:14:47,500 --> 00:14:47,900
Let's go.

292
00:14:48,380 --> 00:14:49,140
Take me to work.

293
00:14:49,260 --> 00:14:49,540
Hey.

