304
00:15:07,580 --> 00:15:08,460
You're so grown up.

305
00:15:08,700 --> 00:15:09,980
Why are you always so touchy?

306
00:15:11,140 --> 00:15:12,780
What's wrong? You're my brother.

307
00:15:12,900 --> 00:15:15,380
