I'll still hug you.

308
00:15:15,700 --> 00:15:16,540
Why shouldn't I?

309
00:15:16,820 --> 00:15:18,020
I'll just keep hugging.

310
00:15:18,020 --> 00:15:18,820
Keep hugging.

311
00:15:21,060 --> 00:15:21,740
Doctor,

312
00:15:21,740 --> 00:15:22,780
I'm discharged.

313
00:15:22,780 --> 00:15:23,940
