316
00:15:26,540 --> 00:15:26,940
Exactly.

317
00:15:27,300 --> 00:15:28,620
She needs to be checked properly.

318
00:15:28,620 --> 00:15:30,430
Why do you have to insist on
going to that silly job?

319
00:15:30,440 --> 00:15:31,520
What's wrong with that?

320
00:15:31,520 --> 00:15:33,100
I think the fever
is making you confused.

321
00:15:33,100 --> 00:15:34,160
Why do you have to insist?

