326
00:16:09,140 --> 00:16:13,020
♪Pear blossoms fall like snow
on your brows♪

327
00:16:13,180 --> 00:16:15,860
♪Memories entwine reality♪

328
00:16:16,140 --> 00:16:20,220
♪The cycle of stars continues,
only you anchor me♪

329
